 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# NER 实验与对比\\n",
    "\\n",
    "对比不同NER方案的效果：规则 vs HanLP vs LLM。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import sys\\n",
    "sys.path.insert(0, '..')\\n",
    "\\n",
    "from src.nlp.ner import NERExtractor\\n",
    "from src.nlp.relation_extract import RelationExtractor\\n",
    "from src.nlp.event_extract import EventExtractor\\n",
    "from src.nlp.summarizer import TextSummarizer\\n",
    "\\n",
    "ner = NERExtractor(engine='rule')\\n",
    "summarizer = TextSummarizer(llm_client=None)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 测试文本\\n",
    "text = '''\\n",
    "北京时间2024年1月16日，字节跳动在深圳举行了年度产品发布会。\\n",
    "CEO梁汝波宣布推出全新的AI助手产品\\\"豆包2.0\\\"，\\n",
    "该产品基于自研的大语言模型，支持多模态交互。\\n",
    "腾讯公司同日表示，其混元大模型已在微信中全面接入。\\n",
    "分析人士认为，中国AI市场正在进入白热化竞争阶段。\\n",
    "'''"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# NER抽取\\n",
    "entities = ner.predict(text)\\n",
    "print('=== 实体列表 ===')\\n",
    "for e in entities:\\n",
    "    print(f'  [{e[\\"type\\"]:6s}] {e[\\"text\\"]:20s} conf={e[\\"confidence\\"]:.2f}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 摘要测试\\n",
    "result = summarizer.summarize(text, max_length=100)\\n",
    "print(f'方法: {result[\\"method\\"]}')\\n",
    "print(f'摘要: {result[\\"summary\\"]}')\\n",
    "print(f'关键点: {result[\\"key_points\\"]}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 实验结论\\n",
    "- 规则NER速度快但覆盖有限\\n",
    "- HanLP可提供更高精度的中文NER\\n",
    "- LLM适合处理歧义实体和复杂关系"
   ]
  }
 ],
